text: The National Party of Australia - Tasmania, also called the Tasmanian Nationals, is the Tasmanian branch of the National Party, a centre-right agrarian party in Australia. Unlike most other states, the Tasmanian Nationals do not currently form the Coalition with the Liberal Party due to the fact that the Nationals hold no seats in the Tasmanian Parliament.
